# Root-level compose overrides. Copy to .env before `docker compose up` if
# you need any of these; the stack runs fine with none of them set.

# Optional. Plain Vision API key (Google Cloud Console -> APIs & Services
# -> Credentials -> Create API key, restrict it to the Vision API), not a
# service-account key file -- many GCP orgs block service-account key
# creation by default. Without this, detection-svc still runs; scans just
# skip the reverse-image-search leg. See
# apps/detection-svc/README.md "What this does not do".
GOOGLE_VISION_API_KEY=
